    ) a

group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
","temp.nmso_bau")

                count(distinct case when NM3SO>11 and NM3SO<=12 and lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end) as 11_12_FB,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>12 and NM3SO<=13 then subOrderId end) as 12_13_SD,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>12 and NM3SO<=13 and lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end) as 12_13_FB,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>13 and NM3SO<=14 then subOrderId end) as 13_14_SD,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>13 and NM3SO<=14 and lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end) as 13_14_FB,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>14 and NM3SO<=15 then subOrderId end) as 14_15_SD,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>14 and NM3SO<=15 and lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end) as 14_15_FB,
